dystopia&lt;/a>; &lt;a title=&quot;tesla&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https://www.tiktok.com/tag/tesla?refer=embed&quot;>;#tesla&lt;/a>; &lt;a title=&quot;cybertruck&quot; target=&quot; _blank&quot; href=&quot;https://www.tiktok.com/tag/cybertruck?refer=embed&quot;>;#cybertruck&lt;/a>; &lt;a title=&quot;rivian&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https://www .tiktok.com/tag/rivian?refer=embed&quot;>;#rivian&lt;/a>; &lt;a title=&quot;cars&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https://www.tiktok.com/tag/cars?refer =embed&quot;>;#cars&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; &lt;a target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;♬ 原声 - Nilay Patel 解码器&quot; href=&quot;https://www.tiktok.com/music/original- sound-7347783441377299242?refer=embed&quot;>;♬ 原声 - Nilay Patel 解码器&lt;/a>; &lt;/section>; &lt;/blockquote>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;CYMSdd&quot;>;“我认为我们真的是未来主义者，流行设计工具公司的创始人 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24102160/figma-ceo-adobe-deal-design-ai-web-future-regulation- sxsw-decoder-interview&quot;>;当被要求比较 Cyber​​truck 时，他在 SXSW 现场录制的 &lt;em>;Decoder&lt;/em>; 中告诉观众...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot; https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/18/24104890/figma-ceo-dylan-field-cyberpunk-solarpunk-trends-sxsw-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/18/24104890/figma-ceo-dylan-field-cyberpunk-solarpunk-trends-sxsw-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/18/24104890/figma-ceo-dylan-field-cyberpunk-solarpunk-trends-sxsw-2024</id><author><name>尼莱·帕特尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-03-18T15:52:02-04:00</published><updated> 2024-03-18T15:52:02-04:00</updated><title>最高法院对限制白宫与社交媒体平台交谈持怀疑态度</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;最高法院大楼与像素化天空的照片插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/CRHpNjJ-QwG35MLNrXHos_3vRfU=/20x0:2021x1334/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73216184/STK463_SCOTUS_B.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Cath Virgin